title: An alternatively spliced transcript, p65 delta 2, of the gene encoding the p65 subunit of the transcription factor NF-kappa B.
abstract_text: We have identified a second alternatively spliced transcript of the NF-kappa B transcription factor p65 subunit. This transcript, named p65 delta 2, varies from p65 at two functionally important regions.
full_text_abstract: We have identified a second alternatively spliced transcript of the NF-kappa B transcription factor p65 subunit. This transcript, named p65 delta 2, varies from p65 at two functionally important regions.
